author: laura.schrettl@kurier.at (Laura Schrettl)
articleTitleTranslated: Almost 5,600 new corona infections in Austria
articleContent: 3.229 Menschen müssen derzeit wegen Covid-19 in Krankenhäusern behandelt werden, davon 474 Patienten auf Intensivstationen.
articleContentTranslated: 3,229 people currently have to be treated in hospitals for Covid-19, 474 of them in intensive care units.
